=Episode 15=

3
00:01:01,550 --> 00:01:03,270
What did you cook today?
It smells so good.

4
00:01:04,150 --> 00:01:05,340
Songyan came back today.

5
00:01:05,660 --> 00:01:06,380
Go ahead.

6
00:01:06,660 --> 00:01:07,790
I have one more dish to make.

7
00:01:10,020 --> 00:01:11,150
Finally willing to come home.

8
00:01:15,580 --> 00:01:16,550
Still mad at me?

9
00:01:17,550 --> 00:01:18,030
In the past,

10
00:01:18,310 --> 00:01:19,780
