137
00:07:19,430 --> 00:07:20,750
I understand how you feel.

138
00:07:21,070 --> 00:07:22,630
We're expanding the search area.

139
00:07:22,950 --> 00:07:24,460
But it was raining that night.

140
00:07:24,660 --> 00:07:25,870
No tire tracks,

141
00:07:26,070 --> 00:07:27,070
