142
00:07:27,390 --> 00:07:28,900
This makes our work difficult too.

143
00:07:29,020 --> 00:07:30,340
We have to understand each other.

144
00:07:31,270 --> 00:07:32,430
Qinyang was at the scene.

145
00:07:32,750 --> 00:07:33,540
He's a witness.

146
00:07:34,020 --> 00:07:36,470
He can confirm that the headlights
belonged to a Jinbei van.

147
00:07:36,630 --> 00:07:38,870
Why not check all Jinbei vans
in the city?

148
00:07:39,020 --> 00:07:40,100
It's such an obvious clue.

149
00:07:40,270 --> 00:07:41,190
Of course we checked.

150
00:07:41,510 --> 00:07:43,540
All relevant exits and roads
near the crime scene

151
00:07:43,540 --> 00:07:44,460
were checked,

152
00:07:44,460 --> 00:07:46,540
but no Jinbei vans were seen that night.

153
00:07:47,430 --> 00:07:48,990
We also had other officers

154
00:07:48,990 --> 00:07:50,580
