155
00:07:51,090 --> 00:07:52,630
Children sometimes misremember things.

156
00:07:53,070 --> 00:07:54,510
It's understandable.

157
00:07:59,110 --> 00:08:00,860
The child still insists
it was a Jinbei van.

158
00:08:18,190 --> 00:08:19,220
How is my dad?

159
00:08:19,950 --> 00:08:21,190
He's out of danger for now.

160
00:08:21,830 --> 00:08:23,270
But he needs a few days in the ICU.

161
00:08:26,750 --> 00:08:28,270
You should prepare yourself.

162
00:08:31,660 --> 00:08:32,390
I understand.

